You can simply ask Alexa to control your ParrotUncle Ceiling Fan. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our ParrotUncle Smart app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our ParrotUncle Smart app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search ParrotUncle Smart skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable ParrotUncle Smart skill, and you'll be navigated to ParrotUncle Smart login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, set direction fan to forward/reverse on ParrotUncle Ceiling Fan.”
“Alexa, set the Fan on the ParrotUncle Ceiling Fan to maximum.”
"Alexa, dim the bathroom light."
"Alexa, set the bedroom light to fifty percent."
"Alexa, decrease the color on the ParrotUncle Ceiling Fan by 3."
